research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for The Colony, TX include the Mayor and six City Council members. Designations such as 'Place' and 'At-Large' or 'Single Member District' have been included. Information for Place 4 was prioritized from the official city website and Texas Municipal League over Wikipedia due to potential discrepancies. Joel Marks is the Mayor Pro Tem, and Robyn Holtz is the Deputy Mayor Pro Tem.
